UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='A pleasure doin\' business with ya.$B$BAnd $N, wipe that look of disgust off yer face.' WHERE `entry`=7659;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='Are you headed back into the Scholomance, $N? You\'ve already paid such a great price for the use of the Divination Scryer - perhaps you\'d like to take another one with you. With it, you\'d be able to face the perils of the Great Ossuary once more.$B$BBy all means, have it. You\'ve certainly earned it.' WHERE `entry`=7666;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc9`='Fuel for the Zapping',`objectives_loc9`='Collect 10 Water Elemental Cores from the Sea Elementals and Sea Sprays along the Forgotten Coast of Feralas, and bring them back to Zorbin Fandazzle who is near the dock there.',`offerrewardtext_loc9`='Scrumdillyriffic!  These cores will keep me working for some time. Add to that the benefit of there now being fewer elementals along the coast, and I might no longer cry myself to sleep at the prospect of having set up shop in perhaps the worst place imaginable!$B$BThank you, $N, for your efforts on my behalf. While it certainly straps me financially to do this, allow me to show you some gratitude you may understand and appreciate... loot!' WHERE `entry`=7721;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc9`='Curse These Fat Fingers',`objectives_loc9`='Hansel Heavyhands wants you to kill 20 Heavy War Golems.$B$BThe Heavy War Golems wander the areas surrounding the Cauldron in the Searing Gorge. When you\'ve killed enough, return to Hansel in Searing Gorge.',`offerrewardtext_loc9`='Ye\'re a good lad, ye are. I got ye a lil\' present fer yer troubles.' WHERE `entry`=7723;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc9`='Zukk\'ash Infestation',`details_loc9`='From what scouting we have managed to muster, we believe that the foe south of the gnolls is an insect-like race. Frankly, it is irrelevant whether or not if they\'re sentient. If they are driving the gnolls to frenzy against us, then they are as big of a threat - if not more - than the gnolls.$B$BDrive deep into where these Zukk\'ash insects dwell; it is known as the Writhing Deep. Thin their numbers and report back to me what you find, bringing back their carapaces as evidence of your handiwork.',`offerrewardtext_loc9`='Well done, $C. Though the extensiveness of the Zukk\'ash presence will not be thwarted with anything less than a full-scale invasion, you have bought us some time so we can devise a proper strategy.$B$BI will be sure to have these carapaces analyzed; we\'ll need to learn everything about them before we deal with what has unfortunately turned into a much larger issue than we had anticipated.' WHERE `entry`=7730;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc9`='Stinglasher',`offerrewardtext_loc9`='Impressive, $C... most impressive!  If Stinglasher is indeed one of their strongest creatures, the study of the beast will prove to be quite valuable in time. It\'s now my charge to make sure we defend ourselves long enough to take advantage of it.$B$BPlease accept this coin bounty as a token of the entire camp\'s thanks, $N. Well done.' WHERE `entry`=7731;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='Incredible!  You may have found the granddaddy of all yeti hides with this!$B$BYou better believe I\'ll pay you for it. I normally don\'t pay that much for a single hide, but I\'m pretty sure I can make something special from it. Thanks for thinking of me on this, $N!' WHERE `entry`=7735;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='Keep the residue pouring in!' WHERE `entry`=7737;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc9`='You have found what may very well be a perfect yeti hide. You easily note that it is exceptionally thick and sturdy - more so than even the ones you\'ve seen from the yeti in Rage Scar.$B$BConsidering that Jangdor Swiftstrider at Camp Mojache is in the market for yeti hides, this particular one may be of considerable interest to him.',`objectives_loc9`='Bring the Perfect Yeti Hide to Jangdor Swiftstrider at Camp Mojache, Feralas.',`offerrewardtext_loc9`='This is an incredible find! I believe this is the finest yeti hide specimen I have ever seen!$B$BIndeed, this is certainly worthy of an appropriate bounty. I normally don\'t pay that much for a single hide, but I\'m confident I can make something special from it. Thanks for thinking of me on this, $N!' WHERE `entry`=7738;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='You don\'t even flinch as the smoldering brand is pressed into your flesh. You are so tough!$B$BYou now hold the Mark of Drakkisath. Have fun storming the castle.' WHERE `entry`=7761;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc9`='The old feeling returns. The welcome pangs of victory reverberate throughout your being. Before you lies the monolithic, battle scarred head of Nefarian. Return it to your Highlord, champion.',`objectives_loc9`='Return the Head of Nefarian to Highlord Bolvar Fordragon in Stormwind.',`offerrewardtext_loc9`='You need not be told the meaning of what you have done, $N. This day will be recorded in the annals of history. A victory the likes of which has not been known to the Alliance for years - if ever!' WHERE `entry`=7781;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='<Field Marshal Afrasiabi bows.>$B$BChoose your reward, let the celebration begin!' WHERE `entry`=7782;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc9`='The old feeling returns. The welcome pangs of victory reverberate throughout your being. Before you lies the monolithic, battle scarred head of Nefarian. Return it to your Warchief, champion.',`objectives_loc9`='Return the Head of Nefarian to Thrall in Orgrimmar.',`offerrewardtext_loc9`='You have honored the Horde once more, $N. The son of Deathwing lays dead. Surely, the evil one stirs.' WHERE `entry`=7783;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc9`='Seek out High Overlord Saurfang in the Valley of Strength.',`objectives_loc9`='Speak with High Overlord Saurfang in Orgrimmar. He stands waiting for you in the Valley of Strength.',`offerrewardtext_loc9`='Choose your reward so that I may mount the head of the beast for all to see.' WHERE `entry`=7784;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc9`='Examine the Vessel',`offerrewardtext_loc9`='May you be protected in your crusade. May the Master bless your efforts.' WHERE `entry`=7785;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc9`='Thunderaan the Windseeker',`objectives_loc9`='To free Thunderaan the Windseeker from his prison, you must present the right and left halves of the Bindings of the Windseeker, 10 bars of Elementium, and the Essence of the Firelord to Highlord Demitrian in Silithus.',`offerrewardtext_loc9`='Even in dreams I did not dare foresee this day.$B$BBehold, mortal.$B$BBEHOLD HE WHO IS OLDER THAN EXISTENCE!$B$BBEHOLD HE WHO HAS FACED TITAN AND GOD ALIKE!$B$BRISE MY MASTER! BREAK FROM YOUR BONDS!' WHERE `entry`=7786;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc9`='Rise, Thunderfury!',`offerrewardtext_loc9`='Please do not harm me! Take it! Take the blade! Leave Demitrian to reshape his pathetic life!' WHERE `entry`=7787;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='Wonderful! We thank you for your generous donation, $N!' WHERE `entry`=7791;
