UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='Hurry up and turn those in if you want to be declared the Master Angler!  I have been standing around here for HOURS with nothing to eat!   Hand those suckers over!' WHERE `entry`=8193;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='This deal works for me if it works for you!' WHERE `entry`=8194;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc9`='I seek the Paragons of Power known as the Coins of the Tribes. They are the currency used by the various denizens of Zul\'Gurub, and each is imbued with subtle but powerful mojo.$B$BThere are nine distinct kinds to be found. Some are sought after by my compatriots for various armors they offer Zandalar heroes. Should you have any extra, I will trade you one of our Honor Tokens for a set of three. You may use the Tokens with Rin\'wosho the Trader; he offers our heroes special items for them.',`offerrewardtext_loc9`='Excellent - this set of coins will make a fine addition to our growing collection... one that we will use in the tribe\'s defense against the rise of the Blood God. You\'ve earned this Honor Token, $N, as well as the thanks of the tribe!' WHERE `entry`=8195;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='A fair trade, my friend - please enjoy the luscious fruits of the South Seas, with the tribe\'s blessing.' WHERE `entry`=8196;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='You gained the heads!  You have halted the plundering of our gods\' power, and weakened Hakkar!$B$BYour actions are truly heroic, $N. May the heads of these troll thralls plead to you for mercy long after their blood chills.' WHERE `entry`=8201;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='*Whir* $B$B Identification of Keefer\'s Angelfish complete. $B$B Your Reward is now available. $B$B *click-click* *Bzzzz*' WHERE `entry`=8221;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='Great job, $N!  Thanks a lot!  I\'m going to make paint from this blood and turn all kinds of cheap junk into glowing treasure!$B$BHere are your tickets, and thanks again!' WHERE `entry`=8222;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='Thanks again, $N. Here are your tickets!' WHERE `entry`=8223;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='*Whir* $B$B Identification of Dezian Queenfish complete. $B$B Your Reward is now available. $B$B *click-click* *Bzzzz*' WHERE `entry`=8224;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='*Whir* Identification of Brownell\'s Racer complete. Your Reward is now available. *click* *click* *Bzzzz*' WHERE `entry`=8225;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='Why, you found my favorite measuring tape! I love this tape! I measured some of the biggest fish I ever caught with it...$B$BBut, I lost this tape in Zul\'Gurub... you\'ve been to Zul\'Gurub? Did you see the fabled Gahz\'ranka?$B$BWell... do you want to catch him?' WHERE `entry`=8227;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc9`='Retrieve the Sealed Azure Bag from the Timbermaw Shaman in Azshara. Then take the bag to Archmage Xylem, also found in Azshara.',`offerrewardtext_loc9`='I see you have Lord Ravenholdt\'s bag. Why didn\'t you say so, boy?' WHERE `entry`=8234;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc9`='I seek the Paragons of Power known as the Coins of the Tribes. They are the currency used by the various denizens of Zul\'Gurub, and each is imbued with subtle but powerful mojo.$B$BThere are nine distinct kinds to be found. Some are sought after by my compatriots for various armors they offer Zandalar heroes. Should you have any extra, I will trade you one of our Honor Tokens for a set of three. You may use the Tokens with Rin\'wosho the Trader; he offers our heroes special items for them.',`offerrewardtext_loc9`='Excellent - this set of coins will make a fine addition to our growing collection... one that we will use in the tribe\'s defense against the rise of the Blood God. You\'ve earned this Honor Token, $N, as well as the thanks of the tribe!' WHERE `entry`=8238;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc9`='I seek the Paragons of Power known as the Coins of the Tribes. They are the currency used by the various denizens of Zul\'Gurub, and each is imbued with subtle but powerful mojo.$B$BThere are nine distinct kinds to be found. Some are sought after by my compatriots for various armors they offer Zandalar heroes. Should you have any extra, I will trade you one of our Honor Tokens for a set of three. You may use the Tokens with Rin\'wosho the Trader; he offers our heroes special items for them.',`offerrewardtext_loc9`='Excellent - this set of coins will make a fine addition to our growing collection... one that we will use in the tribe\'s defense against the rise of the Blood God. You\'ve earned this Honor Token, $N, as well as the thanks of the tribe!' WHERE `entry`=8239;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='Excellent... each bijou we wrest away from the Blood God\'s minions is one step closer we all are to finally defeating them once and for all. You bring honor to the Zandalar - and yourself - through your noble actions.$B$BRemember $N, you may always destroy the bijous you find in Zul\'Gurub at the altar. For each one, you will gain recognition and an Honor Token!  Just remember to have an open space in your inventory if you don\'t have one of the tokens already.' WHERE `entry`=8240;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='May these knives find a place in someone\'s heart.$B$BLiterally.' WHERE `entry`=8249;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc9`='The blood elves in Azshara have developed a method for pulverizing the magical items they acquire. This glittering dust they produce differs from the components normally acquired by a disenchantment spell.$B$BWhen I sent my apprentice to trade for the dust, he was killed without hesitation. For that, they must pay.$B$BThe time for talk is over, $N. Find the blood elves along the cliffs of Azshara and use more "persuasive" methods to acquire their glittering dust.',`objectives_loc9`='Bring 10 Glittering Dust to Archmage Xylem.',`offerrewardtext_loc9`='Well done, $N!  It never ceases to amaze me how persuasive a volley of arcane missiles can be.' WHERE `entry`=8251;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc9`='Cenarion Aid',`details_loc9`='It is the way of the divine to help those in need. The how is insignificant -- only the why matters.$B$BThe Cenarion Circle has such a need. Speak with Ogtinc to lend aid to their plight. He resides atop the cliffs to the northeast of the Ruins of Eldarath in Azshara.',`objectives_loc9`='Seek out Ogtinc in Azshara.' WHERE `entry`=8254;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc9`='Now the last part, the second cure.$B$BThe green drake Morphaz is known to be immune to all forms of poison and disease -- many druids died to bring us this information. There is no doubt his blood is potent for our needs.$B$BA courier from the Cenarion Circle will take the parts you have already collected while you gather the last. Summon your allies and seek out the drake\'s lair in the sunken temple of Atal\'Hakkar. Bring his blood to Greta Mosshoof in Felwood.',`objectives_loc9`='Kill Morphaz in the sunken temple of Atal\'Hakkar, and return his blood to Greta Mosshoof in Felwood. The entrance to the sunken temple can be found in the Swamp of Sorrows.',`offerrewardtext_loc9`='You have slain Morphaz and carried his blood to us... I can hardly believe this good news!$B$BWe will combine the ingredients at once and begin healing the trees and creatures of Felwood. It will take a lifetime to undo what has happened here, but you have given us the means to do it.' WHERE `entry`=8257;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='You\'ve certainly begun to prove yourself to us, $N. As a reward, please take this care package! Inside it you\'ll find rations and bandages that are usable only inside Arathi Basin. $B$BAs you continue to prove yourself inside the Basin, you\'ll find that these items will become available to you for purchase. Rations become available when you are Honored with us, and bandages when you are Revered.' WHERE `entry`=8260;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='You\'ve certainly begun to prove yourself to us, $N. As a reward, please take this care package! Inside it you\'ll find rations and bandages that are usable only inside Arathi Basin. $B$BAs you continue to prove yourself inside the Basin, you\'ll find that these items will become available to you for purchase. Rations become available when you are Honored with us, and bandages when you are Revered.' WHERE `entry`=8261;
