UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc9`='The elemental spirits of this place don\'t be likin\' me any more.$B$BYou know about the totems more than any, and I be needin\' a spirit totem to protect me. We already got the elements, now we need somethin\' more with more nature. More primal.$B$BIn the Western Plaguelands you can kill bears for claws and spiders for their eyes. The carrion birds eat everything, so they might have either one.',`objectives_loc9`='Bring the pieces for the spirit totem to Bath\'rah the Windwatcher.',`offerrewardtext_loc9`='Great, mon! Let\'s try it out...' WHERE `entry`=8412;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc9`='Commander Ashlam Valorfist has sent out a call for a paladin of your purity and valor, $N. You can find him at Chillwind Camp in the southern part of the Western Plaguelands. Seek him and aid in his cause for the Light!',`objectives_loc9`='Speak to Commander Ashlam Valorfist at Chillwind Camp.',`offerrewardtext_loc9`='Very well, $C! Let\'s see what you\'re made of.' WHERE `entry`=8415;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc9`='Your honor has brought some peace to me. It is only right that I offer you something in return.$B$BMy weapons and armor were splendid in life, and yet they are of no use to me now. They would be better served in your possession.$B$BTravel to the sunken temple and destroy the troll guardians Gasher, Mijan, Zolo, Hukku, Zul\'lor, and Loro. They carry magic feathers that can reform my physical body long enough to grant you a reward.',`objectives_loc9`='Bring the Voodoo Feathers from the trolls in the Sunken Temple to the Fallen Hero of the Horde.',`offerrewardtext_loc9`='At last I can feel the cold touch of steel again, even if only for a moment.' WHERE `entry`=8425;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='Excellent! You\'ve shown your worth by defending our operations in Warsong Gulch! May word of your honor spread far and wide across our lands.' WHERE `entry`=8426;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='Excellent! You\'ve shown your worth by defending our operations in Warsong Gulch! May word of your honor spread far and wide across our lands.' WHERE `entry`=8427;
