UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc9`='That\'s an amazing story, $N! You have my thanks, and the heartfelt gratitude of all who were involved. Now maybe I\'ll be able to sleep at night with both eyes shut.$B$BAs to your reward, I believe I have a few things that you\'ll really enjoy.',`objectives_loc9`='Give Deliana your Lightforge Helm and Lightforge Breastplate.',`offerrewardtext_loc9`='I\'m going to miss you, $N. I owe you such a debt of gratitude; I think I\'ll never be able to repay it.$B$BI hope that you enjoy your new head and chest armor, and that it protects you for a long time to come.' WHERE `entry`=9002;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc9`='That\'s an amazing story, $N! You have my thanks, and the heartfelt gratitude of all who were involved. Now maybe I\'ll be able to sleep at night with both eyes shut.$B$BAs to your reward, I believe I have a few things that you\'ll really enjoy.',`objectives_loc9`='Give Deliana your Devout Crown and Devout Robe.',`offerrewardtext_loc9`='I\'m going to miss you, $N. I owe you such a debt of gratitude; I think I\'ll never be able to repay it.$B$BI hope that you enjoy your new head and chest armor, and that it protects you for a long time to come.' WHERE `entry`=9003;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc9`='That\'s an amazing story, $N! You have my thanks, and the heartfelt gratitude of all who were involved. Now maybe I\'ll be able to sleep at night with both eyes shut.$B$BAs to your reward, I believe I have a few things that you\'ll really enjoy.',`objectives_loc9`='Give Deliana your Shadowcraft Cap and Shadowcraft Tunic.',`offerrewardtext_loc9`='I\'m going to miss you, $N. I owe you such a debt of gratitude; I think I\'ll never be able to repay it.$B$BI hope that you enjoy your new head and chest armor, and that it protects you for a long time to come.' WHERE `entry`=9004;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc9`='That\'s an amazing story, $N! You have my thanks, and the heartfelt gratitude of all who were involved. Now maybe I\'ll be able to sleep at night with both eyes shut.$B$BAs to your reward, I believe I have a few things that you\'ll really enjoy.',`objectives_loc9`='Give Deliana your Dreadmist Mask and Dreadmist Robe.',`offerrewardtext_loc9`='I\'m going to miss you, $N. I owe you such a debt of gratitude; I think I\'ll never be able to repay it.$B$BI hope that you enjoy your new head and chest armor, and that it protects you for a long time to come.' WHERE `entry`=9005;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc9`='That\'s an amazing story, $N! You have my thanks, and the heartfelt gratitude of all who were involved. Now maybe I\'ll be able to sleep at night with both eyes shut.$B$BAs to your reward, I believe I have a few things that you\'ll really enjoy.',`objectives_loc9`='Give Deliana your Helm of Valor and Breastplate of Valor.',`offerrewardtext_loc9`='I\'m going to miss you, $N. I owe you such a debt of gratitude; I think I\'ll never be able to repay it.$B$BI hope that you enjoy your new head and chest armor, and that it protects you for a long time to come.' WHERE `entry`=9006;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc9`='A truly amazing story, $N! You have my thanks, and the heartfelt gratitude of all who were involved, I can assure you. Through your efforts we are delivered from the mistakes of our past.$B$BAs to your reward, I believe I have a few things that you have definitely earned and will truly enjoy.',`objectives_loc9`='Give Mokvar your Wildheart Cowl and Wildheart Vest.',`offerrewardtext_loc9`='I will truly miss you, $N. There is a debt that I owe you, which I may never be able to repay.$B$BEnjoy your new head and chest armor. May it protect you for a long time to come, and help you to achieve even greater honor!' WHERE `entry`=9007;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc9`='A truly amazing story, $N! You have my thanks, and the heartfelt gratitude of all who were involved, I can assure you. Through your efforts we are delivered from the mistakes of our past.$B$BAs to your reward, I believe I have a few things that you have definitely earned and will truly enjoy.',`objectives_loc9`='Give Mokvar your Beaststalker\'s Cap and Beaststalker\'s Tunic.',`offerrewardtext_loc9`='I will truly miss you, $N. There is a debt that I owe you, which I may never be able to repay.$B$BEnjoy your new head and chest armor. May it protect you for a long time to come, and help you to achieve even greater honor!' WHERE `entry`=9008;
