UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc9`='It is as I feared -- the toxin is simply too weak for such a powerful creature.$B$BIf we are to create a toxin of high enough potency, you must venture to the bottom of the Temple of Atal\'Hakkar, unlock the secrets of the altar and recover a putrid vine from the guardian there. The temple is dangerous, and it would behoove you to bring friends.$B$BReturn to me when this is done.',`objectives_loc9`='Retrieve a Putrid Vine from the guardian at the bottom of the Sunken Temple and return to Torwa Pathfinder.',`offerrewardtext_loc9`='At last, the toxin can be created in full. I dare not require you to inflict it upon the creature again, as I have asked too much already.$B$BYou have my thanks and respect. May you be well in your travels, $N.' WHERE `entry`=9053;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc9`='I have discovered a use for the carapace of the crypt fiend. I am able to fashion an extremely light and very deadly set of armor by combining the fragments with some of the desecrated magical armors lost in Naxxramas.$B$BBring me the items I require and I shall fashion for you a suit of armor the likes of which has never before been seen in our world!',`objectives_loc9`='Huntsman Leopold at Light\'s Hope Chapel in the Eastern Plaguelands will make a Cryptstalker Tunic if you bring him the following: 1 Desecrated Tunic, 25 Wartorn Chain Scraps, 4 Arcanite Bars and 3 Cured Rugged Hides.',`offerrewardtext_loc9`='Exellent $N !$B , you got everything just as i asked and now i can make a Cryptstalker Tunic.' WHERE `entry`=9054;
