UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='You\'re quite the energetic young woman, aren\'t you?$B$BThis all looks very adequate. You certainly deserve compensation for gathering up all of this for me, and something a little extra I think.$B$BOh, I almost forgot, here\'s an invitation to the party. And, $C, next time that you drop in make sure to dress up in something a little more... festive.' WHERE `entry`=9067;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc9`='Would you honor me by returning the armor of those that fell in the defense of these lands?$B$BThe armor has been desecrated and is undoubtedly being used for evil; however, with wartorn armor scraps, the desecrated armor can be renewed and worn for battle once more.$B$BBring me the remnants of the fallen along with purification materials and Earthshatter shall be yours to don.$B$BSearch Naxxramas.',`objectives_loc9`='Rimblat Earthshatter at Light\'s Hope Chapel in the Eastern Plaguelands will make an Earthshatter Tunic if you bring him the following: 1 Desecrated Tunic, 25 Wartorn Chain Scraps, 4 Arcanite Bars and 3 Cured Rugged Hides.',`offerrewardtext_loc9`='Exellent $N !$B , you got everything just as i asked and now i can make a Earthshatter Tunic.' WHERE `entry`=9068;
