UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='Excellent work, $N. The integrity of our borders must be preserved at all costs!' WHERE `entry`=24224;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc9`='Win a Warsong Gulch battleground match and return to a Horde Warbringer at any Horde capital city, Wintergrasp, Dalaran, or Shattrath.',`objectives_loc9`='Win a Warsong Gulch battleground match and return to a Horde Warbringer at any Horde capital city, Wintergrasp, Dalaran, or Shattrath.',`offerrewardtext_loc9`='The Horde is in your debt, $N. You\'ve made your people proud with your courage in defending our lands.' WHERE `entry`=24225;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='You\'ve brought great honor to the Horde, $N. Your victory today will ensure a thousand victories tomorrow!' WHERE `entry`=24226;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='There is no greater honor than driving invaders from Horde territories. We salute your great courage in aiding our forces today!' WHERE `entry`=24426;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc9`='Win an Alterac Valley battleground match and return to an Alliance Brigadier General at any Alliance capital city, Wintergrasp, Dalaran, or Shattrath.',`objectives_loc9`='Win an Alterac Valley battleground match and return to an Alliance Brigadier General at any Alliance capital city, Wintergrasp, Dalaran, or Shattrath.',`offerrewardtext_loc9`='Just what I wanted to hear!  A victory in Alterac Valley - even a temporary one - is crucial to our overall strategy against the Horde.' WHERE `entry`=24427;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='What? How did you get this? Isn\'t she... Never mind the details, I suppose. You\'ll be wanting one of these baubles as recompense, no doubt.' WHERE `entry`=24428;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc9`='You have accomplished the truly impossible. The brood mother of the Black Dragonflight lies dead at your feet. Seize her head and deliver it to Neeru Fireblade.',`objectives_loc9`='Take the Head of Onyxia to Neeru Fireblade in the Cleft of Shadow.',`offerrewardtext_loc9`='You\'ve brought me the head of someone who is... No, best not to think about it too hard. You\'ll be wanting recompense for your heroic deeds, no doubt.' WHERE `entry`=24429;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='This is quite a find, $N. I can\'t have you selling this to anyone else, so I\'m willing to offer generously.' WHERE `entry`=24431;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='<Mariel accepts the orders and the captured seeing crystal and examines both.>$B$BGood work, $N, and quick thinking. I\'m sure the theft of this trinket won\'t slow them down for long, but I think you\'ve bought us time to warn the leaders of the Horde and Alliance about the impending attacks.' WHERE `entry`=24442;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='Excellent work. Now that this is in our hands, we must get it to Myralion Sunblaze as soon as possible. We can\'t risk the Silver Covenant taking the book from us again.$B$BI\'ll get that tabard back to Shandy and see that he\'s well compensated for his assistance. Once the book is in Myralion\'s hands, the Silver Covenant won\'t be a threat anymore.' WHERE `entry`=24451;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='<Caladis accepts the heavy book and begins leafing through it.>$B$BI knew the symbols on the blade were familiar. The weapon was most certainly forged by the dragons and gifted to one of the mortal races, but which blade is this, and how did it come to rest in Icecrown?' WHERE `entry`=24454;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='You have remade the blade of Quel\'Delar, although Blood-Queen Lana\'thel proclaimed we could not! The blade must still be tempered, but she and her master will not stand in our way!' WHERE `entry`=24461;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='I... I don\'t understand. Tempering the sword should\'ve restored the blade to its original condition. What has happened here?' WHERE `entry`=24476;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='I had not thought it possible for evil to take hold in such a sword, but I suppose it was naive of me. If the greatest of dragonkind\'s creations could be corrupted and turned against them, why not a mere sword?$B$BUther\'s advice is wise, $N, and I would urge you to heed it quickly.' WHERE `entry`=24480;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc9`='They\'ve put our captured soldiers to work in the quarry! Kill their captors and set them free, hero, and do it quickly. We will need their aid when we confront Scourgelord Tyrannus.',`offerrewardtext_loc9`='You\'ve done well this day. With many of the slaves freed and now with access to the forges, it will not be long before I have a strong force to aid in delivering us from Scourgelord Tyrannus and this foul pit.' WHERE `entry`=24498;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc9`='I cannot thank you enough for coming. We\'re severely undermanned to be risking a venture into the citadel, but opportunities like this are too rare to pass up.$B$BI\'m awaiting the arrival of champions from the coliseum, but if your reputation holds true, you should be more than equipped to fight through the forge yourself. Clear the way to the far side and secure the passage to the Pit of Saron. We will need to hold it to move our men further into the citadel.$B$BPlease hurry, $N. We\'re counting on you.',`offerrewardtext_loc9`='Just in time! Thank you, $N.$B$BThe Pit of Saron lies ahead, and if our scouts are correct, past that will be the Halls of Reflection. It is there that Arthas lets his guard down, and it is there that we hope to find a clue to his weakness... or maybe, just maybe, his redemption.' WHERE `entry`=24499;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc9`='Uther knew a great deal about how Arthas might be defeated. It\'s hard to believe that there is much hope of defeating Arthas upon the steps of his own throne. And who will take up the crown of Lich King if it comes to that?$B$BMany questions remain, but the answers that you\'ve uncovered may be critical to ensuring Arthas\' defeat. You need to find Jaina and escape the Lich King while there\'s still time.',`objectives_loc9`='Find Lady Jaina Proudmoore and escape the Halls of Reflection',`offerrewardtext_loc9`='<Jaina is still catching her breath.>$B$BI can barely believe we\'re still alive. It was foolish of me to follow him. I\'ve made that mistake too many times. And you... it was reckless of you to come after me instead of escaping with the information! But... well... thank you. You truly are a hero.$B$BWith Uther\'s guidance, we may stand a chance at defeating Arthas. All the lives lost today were not in vain.' WHERE `entry`=24500;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='Good. $N, I know of you. You\'ll be perfect for these tasks.$B$BWe\'ve been afforded a rare chance to delve into Icecrown Citadel, but we must move quickly if we\'re to avoid Arthas\' notice.' WHERE `entry`=24506;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc9`='They\'ve put our captured soldiers to work in the quarry. Kill their captors and set them free, $C, and do it quickly. We will need their aid when we confront Scourgelord Tyrannus.',`offerrewardtext_loc9`='You\'ve done well this day. With many of the slaves freed and now with access to the forges, it will not be long before I have a strong force to aid in delivering us from Scourgelord Tyrannus and this foul pit.' WHERE `entry`=24507;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='$N! I\'m so glad you\'ve come.$B$BWe\'ve been afforded a rare chance to delve into Icecrown Citadel, but we must move quickly if we\'re to avoid Arthas\' notice.' WHERE `entry`=24510;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc9`='I\'m glad we have someone capable to aid us in this. Delving into the citadel with so few is risky at best, but opportunities like this are too rare to pass up.$B$BI\'m awaiting the arrival of champions from the coliseum, but if your reputation holds true, you should be more than equipped to fight through the forge yourself. Clear the way to the far side and secure the passage to the Pit of Saron. We will need to hold it to move our men further into the Citadel.$B$BBe quick about it, $N. Time is short.',`offerrewardtext_loc9`='Well timed, $C!$B$BThe Pit of Saron lies ahead, and if our scouts are correct, past that will be the Halls of Reflection. It is there that Arthas lets his guard down, and it is there that we hope to find a clue to his weakness... and a route to vengeance long overdue.' WHERE `entry`=24511;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='Admit you to the Sunwell? That\'s impossible! The Sunwell is the most sacred and important site of our people. We have only recently reclaimed it with the help of the Shattered Sun Offensive. It is not a place for tourists or travelers.' WHERE `entry`=24522;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='I confess that I did not expect Thalorien\'s spirit to recognize you as the heir to Quel\'Delar, but I defer to his judgment. You may enter the Sunwell, but I remind you that you are a guest in the most our most sacred of precincts, and you should act accordingly.' WHERE `entry`=24535;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc9`='Get a load of these guys, would ya? Steamwheedle\'s been handling the business of holidays for years, and all of a sudden, these guys bust into the market. They\'re not Steamwheedle; the cartel hired me to get to the bottom of this. Something stinks here and it ain\'t just perfume.$B$BTake this device I brought and go analyze the perfume clouds around the guards. I want to know what they\'re putting in that stuff. Things ain\'t natural.',`offerrewardtext_loc9`='Hey, thanks, kid. Give it over, let\'s take a look. Oh, that ain\'t good.' WHERE `entry`=24536;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc9`='I knew they were up to no good! There\'s some sort of mind-affecting chemical in here, but I can\'t get a handle on it with such a small sample. I need the real stuff.$B$BDon\'t just go over there and buy it! I don\'t want you giving these scumbags one copper. Nah, you gotta get it from the source, discreet-like.$B$BI\'ll disguise you as a package runner. I saw a stockpile guarded by their goons outside the gates. Go run by, and DON\'T stop, or they\'ll make you! They\'ll toss you a crate. Bring it back here.',`offerrewardtext_loc9`='You got it, huh? Good job, kid. Top notch. Let\'s see what we got here.' WHERE `entry`=24541;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc9`='Shadow\'s Edge is among the greatest weapons a $C could hope to obtain.$B$BIs your lust for power sated, $R?$B$B<You feel Mograine\'s penetrating gaze.>$B$BI thought not. A final warning then...$B$BYou now embark on the most treacherous leg of your quest. Bridle your aspirations, for if your aims are impure then your life, your very soul, is forfeit.$B$BThe weapon you hold is but an empty husk, a mere shadow of what it may become. Only by devouring a thousand souls shall its true potential be unlocked.',`objectives_loc9`='Highlord Darion Mograine wants you to use Shadow\'s Edge to slay 1000 of the Lich King\'s minions in Icecrown Citadel. Souls can be obtained in 10 or 25 person difficulty.',`offerrewardtext_loc9`=' You seem to have endured this leg of your trial admirably, $R. Pray that fate continues to smile upon you in your endeavor...' WHERE `entry`=24547;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='These should suffice, $C. Speak to me when Shadow\'s Edge has been thoroughly empowered and I will attempt its completion.' WHERE `entry`=24548;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `title_loc9`='Shadowmourne...',`offerrewardtext_loc9`='Congratulations, $C. Against insurmountable odds, you have weathered the storm. I trust that you shall find your reward proportionate to your conviction...' WHERE `entry`=24549;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='This is unbelievable, $N. You\'ve really done it! All of the quel\'dorei have heard of Thalorien Dawnseeker and Quel\'Delar, but no one ever thought the sword would be restored.' WHERE `entry`=24553;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='<Myralion takes the hilt from you and scrutinizes the artifact.>$B$BThis came from the citadel? What was it doing there? This blade is certainly not of Scourge manufacture.$B$BWeapons of this quality can only be crafted by a few of Azeroth\'s creatures. We will have to consult them and see if they can help us identify it.' WHERE `entry`=24554;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='We must recover that book from the Silver Covenant. Without that book from Krasus, we stand little chance of solving the mystery of the sword in Icecrown or unlocking its power.' WHERE `entry`=24555;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='I knew Shandy would find a way to make it work. Let me get this enchanted and ready for you to use. With any luck, the tabard\'s owner won\'t even know it\'s missing and Shandy will cover the rest of our tracks.' WHERE `entry`=24556;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='<Magister Hathorel reads the captured orders.>$B$BThe agent you intercepted was supposed to deliver the Wyrmrest tome to Icecrown, after meeting with one Arcanist Tybalin inside the Silver Enclave. We have to reclaim that book, $N, and we only have one chance before it leaves the city. We have to work quickly.' WHERE `entry`=24557;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='<Myralion accepts the heavy book and begins leafing through it.>$B$BThose symbols on the blade seemed familiar and now there\'s little wonder why. This is certainly a dragon blade, gifted to one of the mortal races, but which blade is this, and how did it come to rest in Icecrown?' WHERE `entry`=24558;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='You have remade the blade of Quel\'Delar in defiance of that Blood-Queen Lana\'thel\'s pronouncement! Now, the blade must be tempered before we can show her the folly of her words.' WHERE `entry`=24559;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='Tempering the sword should\'ve restored the blade. Why hasn\'t it worked?' WHERE `entry`=24560;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='How can evil take root in such a sword? I would not have thought it possible if the evidence wasn\'t here before my eyes. If the greatest of dragonkind\'s creations could be corrupted and turned against them, why not a mere sword?$B$BI believe Uther is right. You must heed his advice quickly, $N.' WHERE `entry`=24561;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='I hope you understand that I can\'t just admit you to the Sunwell, $N. This is the most sacred place known to the sin\'dorei and we have only recently regained control over it.$B$BYou would raise the hopes of our people with tales of Quel\'Delar? Without proof of the truth of your claims, I see no reason to take you at your word.' WHERE `entry`=24562;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='You truly do carry Quel\'Delar. This is a great day for all of Quel\'Thalas and the sin\'dorei. You have my leave to enter the Sunwell and finish the sword\'s restoration. Keep your head high, $N. The children of Silvermoon have dreamt of this day for years.' WHERE `entry`=24563;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='Am I truly laying my eyes upon the weapon of Thalorien Dawnseeker? This is a wondrous day for the Sunreavers and for all sin\'dorei!' WHERE `entry`=24564;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc9`='<Roka listens with disgust as you tell her why you\'re trying to track down Snivel.>$B$BYou mean I\'ve been under the spell of an alchemist all this time? I can\'t believe I fell for that fraud! If I ever get my hands on that conniving little goblin, I\'ll tear him apart!$B$BIf he\'s finished his errands, he\'s on his way down to the zeppelin tower east of Orgrimmar\'s gates! Whatever you do, $N, you can\'t let him board that zeppelin and get away with all this!$B$BHurry to the zeppelin tower before you miss him!',`objectives_loc9`='Go to the zeppelin tower outside Orgrimmar and question Snivel Rustrocket about the supplies. Return with any evidence he gives you.',`offerrewardtext_loc9`='You got his ledger? Really? That\'s great, $N. There\'s probably loads of good information in here.' WHERE `entry`=24576;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='With Sartharion slain, surely Deathwing and Sinestra\'s plans are now stalled.' WHERE `entry`=24579;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='Word of your success precedes you, $C. Anub\'Rekhan is no more. You did him a great service, $N.' WHERE `entry`=24580;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='That\'s one less thorn in our side. With Noth destroyed, Scourge research into refining the means of creating the undead will grind to a halt.' WHERE `entry`=24581;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='Well done, $C. The Scourge military command out of Naxxramas has been thrown into disarray by Razuvious\'s demise.' WHERE `entry`=24582;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='Children everywhere will sleep easier knowing that Patchwerk is no more.' WHERE `entry`=24583;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='With Malygos defeated, the Nexus War should come to a swift conclusion. You have the gratitude of the Kirin Tor, $N.' WHERE `entry`=24584;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='I never cease to be amazed by the horrors that can be created through the use of technology.' WHERE `entry`=24585;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc9`='Razorscale normally keeps to her aerie near the Colossal Forge in Ulduar. Of late, however, she has been spotted reigning fire down upon lands outside of the titan complex.$B$BThough the broodmother\'s is a sad tale, she poses an imminent threat to all of Northrend. The Council of Six has decreed that Razorscale must die!',`offerrewardtext_loc9`='Now Veranus can finally rest in peace.' WHERE `entry`=24586;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='I trust that you did not have to face too many of his iron construct assistants?' WHERE `entry`=24587;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='The greatest weakness of Ulduar is its masters\' blind faith in their inventions to protect it.' WHERE `entry`=24588;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='All of Azeroth is fortunate that Timear foresaw the Eredar lord\'s arrival and that you were there in time to slay him.' WHERE `entry`=24589;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='The Frozen Throne is without its chief guardian thanks to you. Our attacks upon the Lich King\'s forces will be all the more successful now.' WHERE `entry`=24590;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='Am I truly laying my eyes upon the weapon of Thalorien Dawnseeker? This is a wondrous day for the Sunreavers and for all sin\'dorei!' WHERE `entry`=24594;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='This is unbelievable, $N. You\'ve really done it! All of the quel\'dorei have heard of Thalorien Dawnseeker and Quel\'Delar, but no one ever thought the sword would be restored.' WHERE `entry`=24595;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='Am I truly laying my eyes upon the weapon of Thalorien Dawnseeker? This is a wondrous day for the Sunreavers and for all sin\'dorei!' WHERE `entry`=24596;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc9`='Present a Lovely Charm Bracelet to King Varian Wrynn in Stormwind.',`offerrewardtext_loc9`='My thanks for this Lovely Charm Bracelet.' WHERE `entry`=24597;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='Am I truly laying my eyes upon the weapon of Thalorien Dawnseeker? This is a wondrous day for the Sunreavers and for all sin\'dorei!' WHERE `entry`=24598;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc9`='Did you want to make a Lovely Charm Bracelet for the Lord of Ironforge? I\'m sure he\'d be thrilled.$B$BDo you already have a Lovely Charm Collector\'s Kit?',`objectives_loc9`='Present a Lovely Charm Bracelet to King Magni Bronzebeard in Ironforge.',`offerrewardtext_loc9`='My thanks for this Lovely Charm Bracelet.' WHERE `entry`=24609;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='My thanks for this Lovely Charm Bracelet.' WHERE `entry`=24610;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='My thanks for this Lovely Charm Bracelet.' WHERE `entry`=24611;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc9`='Did you want to make a Lovely Charm Bracelet for the Warchief? I\'m sure he\'d be thrilled.$B$BDo you already have a Lovely Charm Collector\'s Kit?',`objectives_loc9`='Present a Lovely Charm Bracelet to Thrall in Orgrimmar.',`offerrewardtext_loc9`='My thanks for this Lovely Charm Bracelet.' WHERE `entry`=24612;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='My thanks for this Lovely Charm Bracelet.' WHERE `entry`=24613;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc9`='Present a Lovely Charm Bracelet to Cairne Bloodhoof in Thunder Bluff.',`offerrewardtext_loc9`='My thanks for this Lovely Charm Bracelet.' WHERE `entry`=24614;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='My thanks for this Lovely Charm Bracelet.' WHERE `entry`=24615;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='Great work, $N! People will come running to buy Crown perfumes now that they\'ve had a chance to sample their wonders. Here\'s a little something for helping us out.' WHERE `entry`=24629;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='Nice work, $N! People will be buying Crown colognes by the crate-load now that they\'ve had a chance to try them. Here\'s a little something for helping us out.' WHERE `entry`=24635;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='Lovely work, $N! People will be tripping over one another to get Crown chocolates now that they\'ve had a chance to taste those sweet, romantic treats.$B$BHere\'s a little something for helping us out.' WHERE `entry`=24636;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='Good job, kid. You deserve a little somethin\'. And hey, come back tomorrow if you get the time; I might have a job for ya.' WHERE `entry`=24638;
