UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `objectives_loc9`='Kill 5 Crown Underlings and use Snagglebolt\'s Khorium Bomb to destroy one chemical wagon east of Shattrath City in Terokkar Forest, then return to Detective Snap Snagglebolt in Orgrimmar.',`offerrewardtext_loc9`='Good job, kid. You deserve a little somethin\'. And hey, come back tomorrow if you get the time; I might have a job for ya.' WHERE `entry`=24651;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='Good job, kid. You deserve a little somethin\'. And hey, come back tomorrow if you get the time; I might have a job for ya.' WHERE `entry`=24652;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc9`='Get a load of these guys, would ya? Steamwheedle\'s been handling the business of holidays for years, and all of a sudden, these guys bust into the market. They\'re not Steamwheedle; the cartel hired me to get to the bottom of this. Something stinks here and it ain\'t just perfume.$B$BTake this device I brought and go analyze the perfume clouds around the guards. I want to know what they\'re putting in that stuff. Things ain\'t natural.',`offerrewardtext_loc9`='Hey, thanks, kid. Give it over, let\'s take a look.$B$B<He takes the device from you and fiddles with it.>$B$BOh, that ain\'t good.' WHERE `entry`=24655;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `details_loc9`='I knew they were up to no good! There\'s some sort of mind-affecting chemical in here, but I can\'t get a handle on it with such a small sample. I need the real stuff.$B$BDon\'t just go over there and buy it! I don\'t want you giving these scumbags one copper. Nah, you gotta get it from the source, discreet-like.$B$BI\'ll disguise you as a package runner. I saw a stockpile guarded by their goons outside the gates. Go run by, and DON\'T stop, or they\'ll make you! They\'ll toss you a crate. Bring it back here.',`offerrewardtext_loc9`='You got it, huh? Good job, kid. Top notch. Let\'s see what we got here.$B$B<He cracks open the crate and rummages around inside.>' WHERE `entry`=24656;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='You got his ledger? Really? That\'s great, $N. There\'s probably loads of good information in here.' WHERE `entry`=24657;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='Good job, kid. You deserve a little somethin\'. And hey, come back tomorrow if you get the time; I might have a job for ya.' WHERE `entry`=24658;
UPDATE `locales_quest` SET `offerrewardtext_loc9`='Good job, kid. You deserve a little somethin\'. And hey, come back tomorrow if you get the time; I might have a job for ya.' WHERE `entry`=24659;
